pip install pyinstaller
pyinstaller --onefile -w program_name.py          		[dist->program-name->programe_name.exe]

//--onefile flag for making only single exe file instead of many dependacy files in a folder.
//-w flag to open without terminal

to make an installer for windows for your client
download https://nsis.sourceforge.io/Main_Page 
install it ,select "based on zip file"
make zip file of your dist folder "dist.zip"

for linux do it on linux. windows cannot make distributable for linix
